        "TileImage": "$($repository 62755855-8f3c-4588-bcc1-8c30ac5c8314).Image",
        "Description": "Hello 47,\rOur client showed that several employees have been bribed by a multinational criminal group to provide them with internal security intelligence for the bank. Given that a batch of pecious national treasures are temporarily stored here recently, it is necessary for us to take the lead before they succeed.\rIn addition, this client has requested us to kill the current bank CEO for personal purpose and to pay an extra fee of 7 gold bricks in the vault.\rI would leave you to prepare.",
